'''Mythcon 20''' was the twentieth annual [[Mythopoeic Society]] conference. 

*'''Theme:''' "Mythic Elements in Fantasy"
*'''Guests of Honor:''' [[Guy Gavriel Kay]] (fantasy author) and Raymond H. Thompson (Arthurian scholar)
*'''Chairman:''' Lynn J.R. Wytenbroek
